148
00:06:37.065 --> 00:06:38.805
or would benefit from a specific intervention,

149
00:06:39.545 --> 00:06:41.485
and it can't identify specific individuals

150
00:06:41.485 --> 00:06:43.565
who are abusing systems or take enforcement action.

151
00:06:43.585 --> 00:06:46.485
So the focus of the analysis is at that group level,

152
00:06:46.625 --> 00:06:47.685
not that individual level.

